#. Tag: title
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "kqml User's Manual"
msgstr "Manual del usuario de kqml"

#. Tag: date
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "2023-06-10"
msgstr "2023-06-10"

#. Tag: releaseinfo
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plasma 6.0"
msgstr "Plasma 6.0"

#. Tag: productname
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid "KDE Plasma"
msgstr "KDE Plasma"

#. Tag: manvolnum
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>"
msgstr "<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "QML Runtime with KLocalizedContext"
msgstr "Biblioteca QML en tiempo de ejecución con KLocalizedContext"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kqml</command> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-v, --version</"
"option></group> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-h, --help</option></group> "
"<group choice=\"opt\"><option>-d, --domain</option> <replaceable>domain</"
"replaceable></group> <arg choice=\"opt\"><replaceable>files</replaceable>..."
"</arg> <arg choice=\"opt\"><option>--</option> <replaceable>args</"
"replaceable>...</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>kqml</command> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-v, --version</"
"option></group> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-h, --help</option></group> "
"<group choice=\"opt\"><option>-d, --domain</option> <replaceable>dominio</"
"replaceable></group> <arg choice=\"opt\"><replaceable>archivos</"
"replaceable>...</arg> <arg choice=\"opt\"><option>--</option> "
"<replaceable>argumentos</replaceable>...</arg>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Descripción"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kqml</command> is a QML runtime with initialized KLocalizedContext."
msgstr ""
"<command>kqml</command> es una biblioteca QML en tiempo de ejecución con un "
"KLocalizedContext inicializado."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unlike the qml tool that comes with qt-declarative package, kqml initializes "
"KLocalizedContext that allows testing real-world applications and scratch "
"files with i18n calls throughout their code and imported libraries."
msgstr ""
"Al contrario que la herramienta qml que contiene el paquete qt-declarative, "
"kqml inicializa el KLocalizedContext que permite probar aplicaciones reales "
"y archivos de borrador con llamadas i18n en su código fuente y en las "
"bibliotecas importadas."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Opciones"

#. Tag: term
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-v</option>, <option>--version</option>"
msgstr "<option>-v</option>, <option>--version</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays version information."
msgstr "Muestra información de la versión."

#. Tag: term
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-d</option>, <option>--domain</option> <replaceable>domain</"
"replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-d</option>, <option>--domain</option> <replaceable>dominio</"
"replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "The main localization domain."
msgstr "El dominio de localización principal."

#. Tag: term
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-h</option>, <option>--help</option>"
msgstr "<option>-h</option>, <option>--help</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays this help."
msgstr "Muestra esta ayuda."

#. Tag: term
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "<replaceable>files</replaceable>..."
msgstr "<replaceable>archivos</replaceable>..."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Any number of QML files can be loaded. They will share the same engine."
msgstr ""
"Se puede cargar cualquier número de archivos QML. Compartirán el mismo motor."

#. Tag: term
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "<replaceable>args</replaceable>..."
msgstr "<replaceable>argumentos</replaceable>..."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Arguments after '<option>--</option>' are ignored, but passed through to the "
"application.arguments variable in QML."
msgstr ""
"Los argumentos tras «<option>--</option>» se ignoran, aunque se pasan "
"mediante la variable application.arguments en QML."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "See Also"
msgstr "Consulte también"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More detailed user documentation is available from <ulink url=\"help:/plasma-"
"desktop\">help:/plasma-desktop</ulink> (either enter this <acronym>URL</"
"acronym> into &konqueror;, or run <userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> "
"<parameter>help:/plasma-desktop</parameter></userinput>)."
msgstr ""
"Dispone de una documentación de usuario más detallada en <ulink url=\"help:/"
"plasma-desktop\">help:/plasma-desktop</ulink> (puede introducir esta "
"<acronym>URL</acronym> en &konqueror; o ejecutar "
"<userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> <parameter>help:/plasma-desktop</"
"parameter></userinput>)."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Authors"
msgstr "Autores"

